rows.label: tev035101_SEL1011
rows.name: Ask Aalis about recent developments.

rows.label: tev035101_MSG0001
rows.name:
I decided to take a job with a human arms
manufacturer called the Grenada Galactic Group,
you know?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev035101_MSG0002
rows.name:
That makes the Ma-non company Candid & Credible
our direct competitor, I suppose... But you know better
than to use THEIR weapons, don't you?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev035101_MSG0003
rows.name:
I mean, it matters which arms manufacturer's
weapons you BLADEs sling around, doesn't it?
You're practically walking billboards, after all.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev035101_MSG0004
rows.name:
If you have a favorite company, you should gear up
with their products, right? That support lets them grow,
which leads to new and better products.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev035101_MSG0008
rows.name:
The Ma-non clothes I wear are highly functional,
you know?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev035101_MSG0009
rows.name: But Panyar calls them "boring." Can you believe it?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev035101_MSG0010
rows.name:
Are they "boring" because I don't show enough skin?
I may have to press Panyar for a more specific outline
of of her standards, maybe?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev035101_MSG0016
rows.name:
Did you know I work for a human arms manufacturer
called Grenada GG?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev035101_MSG0017
rows.name:
Well, I've been observing shoppers in order to ascertain
what kind of equipment humans prefer, and I think I'm
finally getting the hang of it, perhaps?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev035101_MSG0018
rows.name:
Take these female BLADEs I saw looking at C&C's
protective wear, all right? They were giggling about
how it showed far too too much midriff...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev035101_MSG0019
rows.name:
And while the words they chose were negative, they
were laughing the whole time. Which means we need
our products to show MORE midriff, right?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev035101_MSG0020
rows.name:
All my observations of human tastes are paying off,
aren't they? As soon as I revised our line to show
more skin, the gear's been flying off the shelves.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev035101_MSG0021
rows.name:
Granted, there is less armor coverage now, so we
made up the difference by upgrading our trademark
beam coating, you see?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev035101_MSG0022
rows.name:
Anyway, I wanted to try a similar approach with our
men's line to boost sales, right? But our human
techs shot that down in no time flat.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev035101_MSG0023
rows.name:
I'm afraid I don't understand, though? Why is it so
wonderful to let female parts flop around and not
male parts?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev035101_MSG0011
rows.name:
The ultimate wonder-ware weapon sounds fascinating,
does it not?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev035101_MSG0012
rows.name:
I asked a co-worker about wonder-ware, and he said
it can totally K.O. a human man just by showing it to
them, okay?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev035101_MSG0013
rows.name:
Anyway, Panyar gave me a bottle of strange liquid as
a a thank-you for giving my size measurements,
but I don't know what it is...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev035101_MSG0014
rows.name:
...How's that? It's a bottle of scented "pear-fume"?
Well, how odd.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev035101_MSG0015
rows.name:
Perhaps you use it to temporarily disable the enemy's
olfactory abilities and sneak up on them?[ST:wait ]
